unificationProblem

Class Problem

  • java.lang.Object
    • unificationProblem.Problem

  • public class Problem
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Problem handles the unification problem sets. p - contains unification problem to be solved c - set of neighborhood constraint sigma - set of pre unifiers phi - set of name-class mapping branch - contains branch of the problem when phi splits
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jan-Michael Holzinger & Sophie Hofmanninger
